{
  "texts": [
    "As mentioned below, ChatGPT in foreign language education provides pedagogical flexibility and encourages students to think critically.",
    "Using ChatGPT, a chatbot that produces consistent texts and dialogues, provides rich input and output in multiple languages and fields, and interacts human-like, is highly beneficial in foreign language education.",
    "It is accessible to everyone worldwide as an open resource, and versions up to ChatGPT 3.5 are free, promoting educational equity for students.",
    "The texts it generates are human-like and consistent, seamlessly connecting sentences.",
    "ChatGPT can be helpful as a chatbot in attracting foreign language learners' interest and motivating them."
  ]
}